{"tid":51032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung爆炸驚魂繼續　Wi-Fi名叫Note 7嚇到飛機急降","createTime":"2016-12-23T01:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T06:29:02.000Z","uid":1886,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50b92f2a9bb991553036fbbd499272de9bb00bd0","tid":51032,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:29:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Samsung爆炸驚魂繼續　Wi-Fi名叫Note 7嚇到飛機急降</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSamsung爆炸驚魂令大眾心有餘悸，日前有人在飛機上將Wi-Fi名改做「Galaxy Note 7」，嚇到飛機急降，大批航班延遲、取消。<br />\n<br />\n據 昨日（12月21日） iMore 編輯主管 Serenity Caldwell 在 Twitter 上指，自己的航班因延遲後被取消，經過大約兩小時後問終於可以上機，期間 Caldwell 聽到職員討論，原來是有乘客在一班飛行中的航班上將 Wi-Fi 熱點，設定為「Galaxy Note 7」，機組人員發現後馬上決定飛機緊急降落。<br />\n<br />\n惡作劇的事主其後被帶去問話，然而整個機場的航班升降已經受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-22-2016/34748\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F12-22-2016%2F34748&d=ZmHNpoj58Zsne7T%2F4trR1HvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=3b23e956\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-22-2016/34748</a>"},{"pid":"58ba6a1e3c8ffbc961060459158cd2f75089f6a3","tid":51032,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde701ae17d09fb00dd2cd73b595303e38432a67","tid":51032,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:30:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Samsung爆炸驚魂繼續　Wi-Fi名叫Note 7嚇到飛機急降</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSamsung爆炸驚魂令大眾心有餘悸，日前有人在飛機上將Wi-Fi名改做「Galaxy Note 7」，嚇到飛機急降，大批航班延遲、取消。<br />\n<br />\n據 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前日（12月21日） iMore 編輯主管 Serenity Caldwell 在 Twitter 上指，自己的航班因延遲後被取消，經過大約兩小時後問終於可以上機，期間 Caldwell 聽到職員討論，原來是有乘客在一班飛行中的航班上將 Wi-Fi 熱點，設定為「Galaxy Note 7」，機組人員發現後馬上決定飛機緊急降落。<br />\n<br />\n惡作劇的事主其後被帶去問話，然而整個機場的航班升降已經受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-22-2016/34748\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F12-22-2016%2F34748&d=ZmHNpoj58Zsne7T%2F4trR1HvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=3b23e956\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-22-2016/34748</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"aaf06b27943f9fcfd1e34cedc52e20789bd6e465","tid":51032,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94092a50988f70c79cb13eb6ce109405d5735403","tid":51032,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:33:26.000Z","msg":"俾人捉去臭格都抵死！"},{"pid":"3ab5d6a7bc2c473c705e74080e5a5214a0c6cf8e","tid":51032,"uid":10280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9acbba8ab53eb4674936081d1862f34b73503d4c","tid":51032,"uid":54209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440b45b2428f4112a2b709580c80fcc781ac3389","tid":51032,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:45:10.000Z","msg":"飛機收到電話信號？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9427f11cbfb2c4c6c458a362742eeaf134a1379","tid":51032,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T01:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2